        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 2 Tuckerella weiterschani n. sp. holotype. Layered POL micrograph. Gnathosoma laterally, arrow points to adoral seta. Abbreviations: palp segments: Fe, femur; Ge, genu; Ta, tarsus; Ti, tibia;" ;
